Goal:

	使用 SQLAchemy 做 ORM


Step:

	1. 安裝 flask sqlalchemy
	Linux:~/project # pip install Flask-SQLAlchemy

	2. model.py, app.py, db_create.py


	3. create databae
	Linux:~/project # python create_db.py
	Linux:~/project #ls posts.db

	4. check database
	Linux:~/project # ipython
	> from models import BlogPost
	> posts = BlogPost.query.all()
